c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Jasper Chat and Pi share a solid foundation of core features including Memory, Multilingual. Where Jasper Chat pulls ahead is with exclusive access to File Upload and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Pi uniquely offers Voice Input, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Jasper Chat holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Pi scores 6/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Pi comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Jasper Chat begins at $49/mo. Pi stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Jasper Chat requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
